func:
var commands = flow.get('commands') || []

msg.topic = 'collect'

switch(msg.payload)
{
    case 'Forward':
    case 'Backward':
        commands.push(msg.payload)        
        break
    
    case 'clear':
        commands = []
        break
    
    case 'run':
        msg.topic = 'start'
        break
}
flow.set('commands',commands)
msg.payload = commands
return msg
